        <h2>INF6027: Data Science Project</h2>
        <p>In this project, I explored the question: <strong>"What factor decides popularity the most?"</strong></p>
        <h3>Steps Taken:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Data preprocessing: Cleaning and transforming the Spotify dataset.</li>
            <li>Analysis: Investigating correlations and building prediction models.</li>
            <li>Visualization: Creating charts to show key findings.</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Key Findings:</h3>
        <p>The feature <strong>"Danceability"</strong> has the highest correlation with song popularity, while "Acousticness" has a negative impact.</p>
